room_title: Escape room "The Medieval Adventure" by Can You Escape? in Tampa
room_description: The year is 1115 and The King of Heves has died in battle. Leaving no heir to the throne but always anticipating this day, a secret chamber was created. Only the noblest and smartest in the land will be able to pass the test and be eligible for the throne. Will you pass 'The King's Challenge'?
